{"tid":1798182,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"炒埋一碟做：五大訴求 缺一獨立","createTime":"2019-12-26T04:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T04:58:52.000Z","uid":33904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e72efc7c313bf66a07e411610cb23c998b61d198","tid":1798182,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:52:59.000Z","msg":"獨立、真普選都係想要真自治姐<br />\n成日話「缺一不可」，實際點樣不可？<br />\n<br />\n不可就係沒完沒了同你攬炒，<br />\n炒到你肯比真自治為止，<br />\n你唔比既話，<br />\n我地就搞獨立，<br />\n同你鬥至最後一滴血。<br />\n<br />\n獨立與否從來源於中共一念之間，<br />\n香港人未必有能力可以獨立，<br />\n但係絕對唔會比中共毫髮無損，全身而退。<br />\n<br />\n怕美國唔支持既，<br />\n呢個口號可以放心叫，<br />\n因為佢地係全力支持五大訴求，<br />\n而家講緊缺一先獨立，<br />\n成個責任不在於我地，<br />\n美國或者唔方便支持我地獨立，<br />\n但仍然有最靚介入點去撐五大訴求：佢地話冇既話就要獨立wor，不如你比五大訴求佢地la。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一獨立</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e32f7cab3a7c4c724a87fcafc4330f79e9316b9","tid":1798182,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:55:35.000Z","msg":"香港獨立 唯一出路<br />\n唔敢嗌既人咪唔嗌囉<br />\n敢嗌既捉咪嗌囉"},{"pid":"3b9cfb938c0d9c0886a64a1e5a77d95a11514df6","tid":1798182,"uid":106480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:56:23.000Z","msg":"[警世] 獨立定自治? 中共分化手段之一<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1798099\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1798099</a><br />\n有興趣來睇下"},{"pid":"0a16041ae0569ac1a4d6211991058bd3a9c8abb9","tid":1798182,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T04:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006daca37d40031279f898a9245e41cd5b594d5f","tid":1798182,"uid":201604,"like":1,